definition:
Someone descended from Mushi who was a man of the tribe of Levi living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Exo.6.19; 
 son of: Merari (H4847); 
 brother of: Mahli (H4249) and Jaaziah (H3269); 
 father of: Mahli (H4249H), Eder (H5740A) and Jerimoth (H3406K)
Group of mu.shi (מוּשִׁי "Mushi" H4187) 
 § Mushites, of Mushi "yielding"
 descendants of Mushi, the great grandson of Levi
